What is Rubix

Rubix is a new cloud gaming platform that will allow users to play their own video games without the need for expensive high-end devices, such as consoles or gaming PCs!

Download

02. ——– Your own Cloud Console

How it works

You’ll be able to stream and play your games in real-time! You only need a supported device and Internet connection.

The Rubix app is available to download on Windows PC (Windows 7 x64 or later) and soon on other devices.
